	<h2>Key takeaways</h2>
	<p>
		Data Transparency &amp; User Control ensures that users understand and control how much data their applications consume.
	</p>
	<p>
		Key outcomes include:
	</p>
	<ul class="vf-list vf-list--unordered">
		<li class="vf-list__item">Improved accessibility for low-bandwidth users</li>
		<li class="vf-list__item">Reduced unexpected data usage</li>
		<li class="vf-list__item">Better performance under constrained conditions</li>
		<li class="vf-list__item">Increased user trust and satisfaction</li>
		<li class="vf-list__item">More efficient resource utilisation</li>
	</ul>

